{"tid":165551,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"三葉造型演唱《LaLaLand》歌曲《The Fools Who Dream》上白石萌音盡顯唱功","createTime":"2017-03-21T12:25:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-22T18:01:27.000Z","uid":9573,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ea8dfcd80fe1fe2955cc4b508b7140d40d301275","tid":165551,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T12:25:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63852/58cf594f1dad1.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63852%2F58cf594f1dad1.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=98011478&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n獲得本屆奧斯卡多項大獎的《樂來越愛你》（La La Land）近來在日本進行宣傳，在日本許多歐美電影都會被再度配音成日文版，讓日本民眾更有親近感，因此宣傳人員也找來了上白石萌音來現場演唱《樂來越愛你》中，女主角艾瑪史東試鏡的原版歌曲《The Fools Who Dream》。<br />\n<br />\n▼上白石萌音將髮型綁成宮水三葉的造型，相當清純可愛。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63852/58cf5a8284d24.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63852%2F58cf5a8284d24.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=9290703d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/56x956.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F56x956.jpg&h=7dfaa321&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼上白石萌音現場演唱《樂來越愛你》試鏡的片段，讓許多網友都驚豔 這位19 歲小女孩的實力派唱功，同時她的妹妹「上白石萌歌」也非常會唱，簡直像是家族基因一樣神奇。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/k3WnW7UBcys\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fk3WnW7UBcys&d=P9V%2Fg5HR%2BYIczjwvlITT9P7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=9fc73044\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/k3WnW7UBcys</a><br />\n<br />\n▼讓我們順帶與艾瑪史東的原版《The Fools Who Dream》來作對照。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/UlunjmpaRVU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUlunjmpaRVU&d=P9V%2Fg5HR%2BYIczjwvlITT9P7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=f8cac044\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/UlunjmpaRVU</a><br />\n<br />\n許多日本網友都驚訝上白石萌音的英語發音，完全大多數人印象中的日式英文口音，更不用說她的演唱實力，上白石萌音在演唱完《樂來越愛你》歌曲之後，也表示這讓她更想要去歐美留學，不過依照上白石萌音現在火紅的程度，應該很難從忙碌的行程中抽身。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63852/58cf5a852218a.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63852%2F58cf5a852218a.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=f40317fa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0a054da5359de98e3a7ae27ed15bb36f0ed5884d","tid":165551,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T12:55:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63852/58cf594f1dad1.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63852%2F58cf594f1dad1.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=98011478&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n獲得本屆奧斯卡多項大獎的《樂來越愛你》（La La Land）近來在日本進行宣傳，在日本許多歐美電影都會被再度配音成日文版，讓日本民眾更有親近感，因此宣傳人員也找來了上白石萌音來現場演唱《樂來越愛你》中，女主角艾瑪史東試鏡的原版歌曲《The Fools Who Dream》。<br />\n<br />\n▼上白石萌音將髮型綁成宮水三葉的造型，相當清純可愛。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63852/58cf5a8284d24.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63852%2F58cf5a8284d24.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=9290703d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/56x956.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F56x956.jpg&h=7dfaa321&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼上白石萌音現場演唱《樂來越愛你》試鏡的片段，讓許多網友都驚豔 這位19 歲小女孩的實力派唱功，同時她的妹妹「上白石萌歌」也非常會唱，簡直像是家族基因一樣神奇。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/k3WnW7UBcys\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fk3WnW7UBcys&d=P9V%2Fg5HR%2BYIczjwvlITT9P7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=9fc73044\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/k3WnW7UBcys</a><br />\n<br />\n▼讓我們順帶與艾瑪史東的原版《The Fools Who Dream》來作對